HE is a jack of all trades and is known for his fabulous fashion sense and forgetting his dashing good looks. Maps Maponyane, who is the son of legendary soccer star and sports commentator, Marks Maponyane. There’s basically nothing Maps hasn’t dabbled on, he has his own fashion label, he’s also a seasoned television presenter and a brand ambassador of Investec Bank, Samsung to mention just a few. At just 28-years-old, he has built himself sprawling home – something he says he has always wanted. “I've wanted this so bad. Home. Finally.” he tweeted next to pictures of his old home and the newly decorated one.  